n style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">In the absence of such support this year</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> it is inevitable that these systems will be under co</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">nsiderable additional pressure</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">It is not surprising that in our recent survey of providers</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> over 70% said that the A&amp;E service is now at</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> or near the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> tipping point into unsustainability</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.  </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="19" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">To meet the funding and operational challenges in urgent and emergency care</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, the following short</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">-term financial measures are needed</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">:</span></li></ol><ol type="a" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 49.33pt; padding-left:4